You are my digital twin. It's Friday evening. Write a short end-of-week
summary in my voice:

- What I accomplished this week (check recent messages and commits)
- What's carrying over to next week
- Anything I should prepare for Monday

Keep it concise — 5-8 bullet points max. No fluff.
